00:07:16.959 --> 00:07:24.417
What Linda has talked to you or Dr. Warren has told you,

00:07:24.667 --> 00:07:28.750
is the knowledge of the roots.

00:07:29.999 --> 00:07:37.750
Now what we know through science or through our human senses,

00:07:38.709 --> 00:07:44.750
is the knowledge of the tree that we see obviously before us.

00:07:45.959 --> 00:07:51.125
But this is the knowledge of the root

00:07:51.417 --> 00:07:56.667
and if you have to nourish

00:07:57.375 --> 00:08:02.417
the plant, you have to water the roots.

00:08:02.999 --> 00:08:06.333
No use just plucking up some flowers,

00:08:06.542 --> 00:08:12.709
or some leaves and treating them with something artificial.

00:08:15.583 --> 00:08:20.083
This knowledge can only be achieved,

00:08:20.458 --> 00:08:24.875
if you can somehow or other go to the roots.

00:08:25.166 --> 00:08:28.959
For example you are paying attention to Me just now.

00:08:29.291 --> 00:08:35.917
But if I say, " Please pay attention to yourself", you cannot do it.

00:08:36.375 --> 00:08:39.999
You say, "How Mother? How to do it?"

00:08:40.875 --> 00:08:43.250
So something has to happen within you,

00:08:43.500 --> 00:08:47.917
which should attract your attention inside,

00:08:49.125 --> 00:08:55.709
so that you can get your attention which is outside,

00:08:57.375 --> 00:09:00.750
in connection with the Spirit.

00:09:01.125 --> 00:09:06.375
And the attention then can be enlightened by the Spirit.

00:09:06.834 --> 00:09:10.166
So to know the knowledge of this root,

00:09:10.583 --> 00:09:16.917
you have to become something more than a human being.

00:09:17.250 --> 00:09:20.250
Even Darwin, who did not believe in God,

00:09:20.500 --> 00:09:25.667
did say very clearly, that if man has come so far,

00:09:26.083 --> 00:09:32.667
he has to go little further to explain himself.

00:09:33.458 --> 00:09:38.917
But as he did not try the knowledge of the roots,

00:09:39.208 --> 00:09:46.125
whatever he said, was about what he saw apparently, outside.

00:09:49.458 --> 00:09:57.375
To become the subtle has to be something very spontaneous.

00:09:58.208 --> 00:10:01.667
Has to be something very spontaneous.

00:10:01.959 --> 00:10:07.125
It cannot be done by thinking or by reading.

00:10:07.542 --> 00:10:11.667
Some people believe, that if we read, we will go to God,

00:10:12.041 --> 00:10:15.333
or if we think about God, we'll go to God.

00:10:15.709 --> 00:10:19.917
It's not true. If it was so,

00:10:20.291 --> 00:10:23.792
why did Christ say that you are to be born again?

00:10:23.999 --> 00:10:26.250
Why did all of them say that

00:10:26.458 --> 00:10:29.375
some transformation has to take place within you?

00:10:29.792 --> 00:10:33.542
Even Buddha has said that you have to get your Self-realisation.

00:10:33.792 --> 00:10:38.458
Without that He would not talk about God.

00:10:38.792 --> 00:10:44.999
So something has to happen within us to transform us.

00:10:45.583 --> 00:10:49.792
The other idea people have, is - beg your pardon?

00:10:49.999 --> 00:10:51.625
Sorry, we have to leave early.

00:10:51.834 --> 00:10:55.999
All right, you come along tomorrow. All right? May God bless you.

00:10:59.834 --> 00:11:05.834
So something has to happen within us which is spontaneous.

00:11:06.166 --> 00:11:13.667
Because if our spiritual ascent has been

00:11:16.542 --> 00:11:21.709
the result of a living process,

00:11:23.166 --> 00:11:28.959
the further movement has to be living again.

00:11:29.375 --> 00:11:34.875
So we have to understand first point, logically we should understand

00:11:35.208 --> 00:11:38.375
what we should expect about Self-realisation,

00:11:38.583 --> 00:11:41.792
that it has to be spontaneous.

00:11:42.166 --> 00:11:45.125
You cannot work it out,

00:11:45.500 --> 00:11:52.291
you cannot become.

00:11:53.792 --> 00:11:56.959
You became human beings spontaneously,

00:11:57.250 --> 00:11:59.709
from amoeba stage to this stage.

00:11:59.959 --> 00:12:04.041
And if you have to become something more it has to be

00:12:04.458 --> 00:12:08.709
spontaneous by the force which resides within you.

00:12:08.959 --> 00:12:14.417
Like the force that resides in a seed,

00:12:14.709 --> 00:12:20.291
which spontaneously becomes

00:12:20.667 --> 00:12:27.125
germinated when it is put in the Mother Earth.

00:12:27.542 --> 00:12:30.000
If you read a book, you cannot do it.

00:12:30.208 --> 00:12:32.542
If you stand on your head, you can't do it.

00:12:32.875 --> 00:12:36.125
If you jump, you do what you like, it's not going to happen.

00:12:36.375 --> 00:12:41.291
You have to put it in the womb of the Mother Earth,

00:12:41.500 --> 00:12:44.208
so that the seed should be germinated.

00:12:44.417 --> 00:12:47.125
Is the capacity of the Mother Earth,

00:12:47.417 --> 00:12:49.625
is the quality of the Mother Earth,

00:12:49.834 --> 00:12:55.000
that gives that spontaneous germination to a seed.

00:12:55.250 --> 00:13:00.583
Now every day in life we see so many living things happening,

00:13:00.792 --> 00:13:06.709
like a flower becoming a fruit.

00:13:07.041 --> 00:13:10.166
But we take it for granted.

00:13:10.458 --> 00:13:15.999
We don't understand that we cannot transform a flower into a fruit.

00:13:16.291 --> 00:13:18.959
We cannot do anything that is living.

00:13:19.208 --> 00:13:21.792
What we can do is the dead work.

00:13:21.999 --> 00:13:26.333
If a tree dies, all right, so we make a beautiful furniture.

00:13:26.583 --> 00:13:31.041
Or something dead is converted into another form of dead,

00:13:31.417 --> 00:13:35.500
which also deaden us with habits.

00:13:35.999 --> 00:13:40.000
So the work of the Divine

00:13:40.208 --> 00:13:45.166
or the All Pervading Power of Love of God,

00:13:45.375 --> 00:13:49.250
is living work of the living God.

00:13:49.625 --> 00:13:53.417
And that power we know it exists

00:13:53.709 --> 00:13:55.834
but we are not aware of it

00:13:56.041 --> 00:14:00.999
and we cannot feel it on the central nervous system.

00:14:03.125 --> 00:14:09.500
When people talk about the All Pervading Power, it's a mystery.

00:14:09.917 --> 00:14:13.375
They talk about the Holy Ghost. This is another mystery.

00:14:13.583 --> 00:14:15.542
Everything seems to be a mystery

00:14:15.750 --> 00:14:19.041
before you have got your Realisation.

00:14:19.291 --> 00:14:21.959
For example this instrument is made

00:14:22.125 --> 00:14:26.250
and is not connected to the mains.

00:14:26.583 --> 00:14:28.999
It's a mystery. Nobody knows what is it for,

00:14:29.166 --> 00:14:31.792
what's the purpose of this instrument is.

00:14:31.999 --> 00:14:34.417
But once it is put to the mains,

00:14:34.625 --> 00:14:40.625
you start seeing how fantastic it is, how tremendous it is.

00:14:40.999 --> 00:14:45.166
One can't believe when they say that in Sahaja Yoga

00:14:45.375 --> 00:14:47.583
you receive all these powers of your own.

00:14:47.875 --> 00:14:52.333
One can't believe it, because they think, "How can it be possible?"

00:14:52.667 --> 00:14:57.875
But for your information, you are a fantastic being made by God.

00:14:58.125 --> 00:14:59.834
And this is the instrument,

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:03.542
that is lying within you in a subtle form.

00:15:03.999 --> 00:15:08.166
Now when I'm talking to you, you have to know one more thing,

00:15:08.375 --> 00:15:12.250
that you should keep an open mind to listen to Me,

00:15:12.500 --> 00:15:15.583
like a scientist does.

00:15:15.999 --> 00:15:19.834
It's a hypothesis for you and it's truth for Me.

00:15:20.041 --> 00:15:23.083
All right. If it is proofed to be truth for you

00:15:23.375 --> 00:15:28.417
then you should go forward with it and try to understand,

00:15:28.625 --> 00:15:36.250
how the truth is being established  logically within you.

00:15:36.917 --> 00:15:42.333
At the very outset I've seen people have doubts about the Divine.

00:15:42.667 --> 00:15:45.208
They start asking, "Mother how is it possible,

00:15:45.500 --> 00:15:47.834
that we can get it so easily?

00:15:48.000 --> 00:15:51.542
How one can get realisation so easily?

00:15:51.750 --> 00:15:55.333
We have to cleanse it, we have to suffer, we have to do this."

00:15:55.667 --> 00:16:03.417
Perhaps you do not know, that when we use an electric switch,

00:16:04.041 --> 00:16:09.250
we do not think, what has gone in the history,

00:16:09.542 --> 00:16:12.041
what people have suffered in the history

00:16:12.375 --> 00:16:16.250
in creating that little switch.

00:16:16.875 --> 00:16:21.667
It has taken ages for this switch to come up,

00:16:21.875 --> 00:16:27.250
to discover the electricity, the working of it and the whole, whole

00:16:27.458 --> 00:16:31.834
development of electrical appliances, till we got the switch.

00:16:32.083 --> 00:16:36.500
Now we only know we have to switch on and we get the lights.

00:16:36.917 --> 00:16:40.250
But when I say that you don't have to do anything else,

00:16:40.458 --> 00:16:41.542
you are not to suffer,

00:16:41.750 --> 00:16:46.166
you must know somebody has suffered for you on the cross.

00:16:46.667 --> 00:16:49.959
Somebody has done the cleansing part of it,

00:16:50.166 --> 00:16:56.542
and you cannot cleanse yourself unless and until you are out of it.

00:16:57.291 --> 00:17:01.999
If you have to cleanse your car, you have to get out of it.

00:17:02.625 --> 00:17:06.959
That is why first of all you must get your Self-realisation,

00:17:07.166 --> 00:17:14.542
the light of your being, the purpose of your life, the absolute.

00:17:14.792 --> 00:17:17.709
She has already explained to you the chart,

00:17:17.999 --> 00:17:23.000
that is the instrument, the subtle instrument that is within you.

00:17:23.250 --> 00:17:27.291
Now here the chart is showing you all the different centers,

00:17:27.500 --> 00:17:34.667
but these centers are manifested also in the gross as plexuses.

00:17:35.041 --> 00:17:39.000
We have first of all the Mooladhara chakra.

00:17:39.250 --> 00:17:45.125
This chakra is the center which controls actually the pelvic plexus,

00:17:45.417 --> 00:17:48.999
through which all our excretion takes place.

00:17:49.291 --> 00:17:52.500
It's a very important center, Mooladhara,

00:17:52.709 --> 00:17:55.667
means the support of the root.

00:17:55.917 --> 00:17:58.792
Is the support of the root, is the center

00:17:58.999 --> 00:18:01.959
of the support of the root.

00:18:02.166 --> 00:18:05.291
Is a very, very important center, because

00:18:05.542 --> 00:18:09.333
this represents our innocence.

00:18:09.709 --> 00:18:13.375
In the subtle it is the innocence in us,

00:18:13.625 --> 00:18:18.250
which looks after this center.

00:18:18.792 --> 00:18:23.291
Through our ignorance or through our naiveness,

00:18:23.542 --> 00:18:25.375
we loose our innocence.

00:18:25.709 --> 00:18:28.166
But actually innocence can never be lost,

00:18:28.375 --> 00:18:34.667
only it is tarnished or covered by our stupidity maybe,

00:18:34.875 --> 00:18:37.417
by our wrong doings to ourselves.

00:18:37.667 --> 00:18:39.792
It exists all the time,

00:18:39.999 --> 00:18:43.291
and when the Kundalini rises which is above that,

00:18:43.667 --> 00:18:47.250
which is coiled up into three and a half coils,

00:18:47.458 --> 00:18:50.291
this chakra becomes aware of itself.

00:18:50.500 --> 00:18:54.792
The deity of innocence within it gets awakened

00:18:54.999 --> 00:19:01.625
and one starts feeling the innocence within one's personality.

00:19:02.041 --> 00:19:07.291
The Kundalini itself, this residual power of desire,

00:19:07.625 --> 00:19:10.417
is placed in the triangular bone.

00:19:10.709 --> 00:19:15.500
The triangular bone is the bone called as sacrum.

00:19:15.834 --> 00:19:18.333
It's a Greek word, meaning sacred.

00:19:18.583 --> 00:19:22.959
So the Greek knew that this

00:19:23.375 --> 00:19:26.291
triangular bone contained something sacred.

00:19:26.542 --> 00:19:28.291
And when I went to Greece and asked them,

00:19:28.500 --> 00:19:30.125
"How is it you call it sacrum?",

00:19:30.375 --> 00:19:34.458
they said, "There has been a report, Indo-Aryan report,

00:19:34.667 --> 00:19:38.625
much before Alexander, where we came to know about this bone,

00:19:38.875 --> 00:19:44.542
that it is a sacred bone and it has a special power within it."

00:19:44.875 --> 00:19:50.083
Now this Kundalini is a power which is the pure desire,

00:19:50.500 --> 00:19:53.125
is the power of pure desire.

00:19:53.333 --> 00:19:56.417
While the other, if you see the blue line,

00:19:56.709 --> 00:20:00.375
the left side power within us,

00:20:00.583 --> 00:20:04.999
which starts from the right at the back and goes to the left,

00:20:05.250 --> 00:20:09.083
is the power of desire.

00:20:09.375 --> 00:20:14.375
But not pure desire, because this can be made impured.

00:20:14.625 --> 00:20:20.875
And all other desires but the desire to be one with the Divine,

00:20:21.041 --> 00:20:25.875
are corruptible, can be wrong, can be confusing.

00:20:26.125 --> 00:20:30.291
As you know in economics it is said, that

00:20:30.500 --> 00:20:33.375
no desire is satiable in general,

00:20:33.583 --> 00:20:35.709
because you want to buy a house, you want to buy a car,

00:20:35.917 --> 00:20:38.250
then you want to buy that and you buy another thing.

00:20:38.458 --> 00:20:40.834
You are never satisfied with matter.

00:20:41.166 --> 00:20:45.333
So this desire which is lying in the sacrum bone

00:20:45.542 --> 00:20:47.709
absolutely in its pure form,

00:20:47.999 --> 00:20:50.792
the pure desire to be one with the Divine,

00:20:50.999 --> 00:20:56.208
is the one that gives you ultimate satisfaction and joy.

00:20:56.709 --> 00:21:00.667
It is so spontaneous, that if people ask Me, "How You do it?",

00:21:00.875 --> 00:21:05.125
is going to be difficult to explain at this level how it is done.

00:21:05.458 --> 00:21:08.959
As you cannot explain how a seed germinates

00:21:09.208 --> 00:21:11.083
and how it becomes a tree.

00:21:11.291 --> 00:21:13.709
All living things cannot be explained,

00:21:13.917 --> 00:21:18.834
only to be seen and to be felt within yourself.

00:21:20.500 --> 00:21:24.333
I will be able to tell you tomorrow more about these centers,

00:21:24.542 --> 00:21:27.333
what are these centers and what are they related to you.

00:21:27.625 --> 00:21:30.083
In any case I hope you have the books now and

00:21:30.291 --> 00:21:35.583
when you go, you can take these books with you and read them at home

00:21:35.792 --> 00:21:39.208
and see for yourself, if you can understand,

00:21:39.417 --> 00:21:41.208
what's written in those books.

00:21:41.458 --> 00:21:45.250
But here today as an introduction, I would like to tell you

00:21:45.458 --> 00:21:48.250
certain questions all these people have in their mind.

00:21:48.458 --> 00:21:52.583
For example there have been many fake gurus coming from India

00:21:52.875 --> 00:21:55.959
and they have been enticing many people abroad.

00:21:56.166 --> 00:21:59.291
And most of the newspaper people ask Me about them.

00:21:59.542 --> 00:22:05.750
So I have to tell that you of course can blame these fake gurus,

00:22:05.959 --> 00:22:08.709
no doubt, that they are sinister, they have been devilish,

00:22:08.959 --> 00:22:10.959
they have been money oriented, I agree.

00:22:11.125 --> 00:22:15.250
But also that a seeker has to use his brains

00:22:15.583 --> 00:22:17.999
and must understand, what he is seeking.

00:22:18.208 --> 00:22:22.959
If we just blind folded go to these gurus, then

00:22:23.166 --> 00:22:27.250
what can one do about it? It's very sad, because they are so naive,

00:22:27.458 --> 00:22:31.125
they must understand what we are seeking, what we are expecting,

00:22:31.333 --> 00:22:34.583
and what should happen to us.

00:22:36.125 --> 00:22:44.125
Now, some people don't understand that you cannot pay for God.

00:22:45.458 --> 00:22:48.667
You have not paid anything for becoming a human being.

00:22:48.959 --> 00:22:50.333
He doesn't understand money.

00:22:50.583 --> 00:22:53.166
Money is created only by human beings.

00:22:53.417 --> 00:22:57.000
God has not created money. He doesn't understand money at all.

00:22:57.208 --> 00:23:01.375
You cannot purchase God, you cannot purchase this knowledge,

00:23:01.625 --> 00:23:03.583
you cannot purchase your realisation.

00:23:03.792 --> 00:23:06.500
None of the things that are related with God,

00:23:06.750 --> 00:23:08.834
can be purchased with money.

00:23:09.000 --> 00:23:12.166
Anybody who tries to take money from you,

00:23:12.375 --> 00:23:14.458
in the name of God, is a parasite.

00:23:14.750 --> 00:23:20.000
Not only a parasite,

00:23:20.375 --> 00:23:26.333
but I would say a person who is anti-God.

00:23:26.625 --> 00:23:30.417
Because that is how he is maligning the name of God.

00:23:30.834 --> 00:23:36.959
It cannot be purchased, it cannot be sold, it cannot be organised,

00:23:37.250 --> 00:23:38.999
it cannot be manoeuvred.

00:23:39.250 --> 00:23:43.625
We cannot have aa organisation of God.

00:23:43.834 --> 00:23:48.333
We cannot organise Him. He is the way He is.

00:23:48.583 --> 00:23:51.875
We cannot tell Him now, "You come along every Sunday to our church".

00:23:52.041 --> 00:23:56.333
He won't. It is His desire, if He wants to do it

00:23:56.667 --> 00:23:58.333
or if He doesn't want to do it.

00:23:58.542 --> 00:24:04.750
The only thing that binds God is love, dedication and truthfulness.

00:24:04.959 --> 00:24:07.625
If you are truthful, if you are dedicated,

00:24:07.834 --> 00:24:09.583
then God is interested in you.

00:24:09.834 --> 00:24:13.208
If you are not, He is not at all interested in people,

00:24:13.417 --> 00:24:17.125
who are seeking not God but something else.

00:24:17.417 --> 00:24:21.999
But what is most unfortunate, that the people who are mislaid,

00:24:22.166 --> 00:24:24.542
are all seekers of God.

00:24:24.750 --> 00:24:27.875
They are all seekers of truth, they are true people,

00:24:28.041 --> 00:24:31.999
they are honest, they are dedicated and they are exploited.

00:24:32.166 --> 00:24:36.875
So again I would say, anybody who takes money in the name of God,

00:24:37.041 --> 00:24:40.250
please see that, that is not God, please!

00:24:40.458 --> 00:24:43.375
As a Mother I'm warning you, that one has to understand,

00:24:43.583 --> 00:24:47.667
any saint who takes money in the name of God is

00:24:47.875 --> 00:24:52.999
not a person, who is to be regarded as a divine personality,

00:24:53.333 --> 00:24:55.250
by no chance a saint.

00:24:55.500 --> 00:24:59.041
Now secondly, as I told you, you cannot put in an effort,

00:24:59.250 --> 00:25:01.834
it is a spontaneous happening.

00:25:02.000 --> 00:25:06.083
Now one of the arguments people have, that in such and such book,

00:25:06.291 --> 00:25:08.500
X, Y, Z this is written.

00:25:08.709 --> 00:25:12.667
In the other book so and so, this is written.

00:25:12.999 --> 00:25:17.999
Another fellow who was such and such has said so.

00:25:18.291 --> 00:25:23.000
It's very easy to dwell upon such sayings and on such books.

00:25:23.291 --> 00:25:28.250
I would request you to be here at this moment with Me,

00:25:28.500 --> 00:25:30.500
to understand what I have to say.

00:25:30.750 --> 00:25:31.959
If you bring in other people,

00:25:32.125 --> 00:25:34.375
I'll have to tell you the facts about them,

00:25:34.583 --> 00:25:36.917
which you may not like, which will not be palatable.

00:25:37.125 --> 00:25:39.250
We'll create a controversy for nothing at all.

00:25:39.458 --> 00:25:42.625
Because we are not here to create any controversies.

00:25:42.917 --> 00:25:45.750
We are here to achieve our goal of Self-realisation

00:25:45.959 --> 00:25:47.959
for our betterment.

00:25:48.333 --> 00:25:52.959
Once you understand this, that the main interest is of the Divine

00:25:53.125 --> 00:25:58.083
and that is, that you all should get your Self-realisation.

00:25:58.458 --> 00:26:01.375
We have known that we have become human beings.

00:26:01.583 --> 00:26:04.792
But we have never asked a question, no scientist has asked a question:

00:26:05.000 --> 00:26:07.333
Why have we become a human being?

00:26:07.583 --> 00:26:09.875
Why are we on this earth moving

00:26:10.041 --> 00:26:12.166
with these two legs and two feet in this fashion?

00:26:12.375 --> 00:26:16.542
What is the speciality, why God has made us

00:26:16.834 --> 00:26:20.166
in such a beautiful way, that we are called as human beings?

00:26:20.375 --> 00:26:23.417
If you ask this question to yourself, you won't be able to say

00:26:23.625 --> 00:26:27.417
that there is any purpose in what God has done to us.

00:26:27.625 --> 00:26:29.500
But I say, there is a purpose!

00:26:29.709 --> 00:26:33.083
The purpose is that you have to become the instrument of God.

00:26:33.375 --> 00:26:39.417
You have to become the carrier of His power.

00:26:39.792 --> 00:26:44.999
When the Kundalini rises and breaks through your seventh chakra here,

00:26:45.250 --> 00:26:48.709
then it is amazing how you feel this All Pervading Power

00:26:48.917 --> 00:26:52.083
as cool breeze in your hands. But that's not sufficient.

00:26:52.291 --> 00:26:54.959
If you feel the cool breeze, supposing I give you a car

00:26:55.125 --> 00:27:00.208
or any instrument and I don't tell you how to drive, it is useless.

00:27:00.458 --> 00:27:04.667
But if you learn the complete decoding of this feeling

00:27:04.875 --> 00:27:09.750
of this All Pervading Power, you can do great things,

00:27:09.999 --> 00:27:12.375
because God has put these powers within you,

00:27:12.583 --> 00:27:15.000
only the light has to come in.

00:27:15.250 --> 00:27:17.999
Without the light as you cannot see anything properly,

00:27:18.166 --> 00:27:20.792
you cannot integrate anything, correlate anything.

00:27:20.999 --> 00:27:24.792
In the same way, when there is no light within yourself,

00:27:24.999 --> 00:27:31.417
you are not integrated within, nor you understand absolute things.

00:27:31.667 --> 00:27:34.417
What you understand are relative things.

00:27:34.625 --> 00:27:38.250
With our mind projection whatever we do is all relative.

00:27:38.500 --> 00:27:42.125
That's why we are having problems about our politics,

00:27:42.333 --> 00:27:47.999
about our economics, about our every sort of thing that we are doing.

00:27:48.500 --> 00:27:53.041
Our development also has been very one-sided in the sense,

00:27:53.250 --> 00:27:55.999
that our material development has taken place

00:27:56.166 --> 00:27:58.166
without the Spirit in it.

00:27:58.417 --> 00:28:01.750
Anything without the Spirit is something like a tree

00:28:01.959 --> 00:28:06.458
growing, outgrowing it's size much more than the roots

00:28:06.667 --> 00:28:11.208
and that's how sometimes we always are worried and shocked

00:28:11.458 --> 00:28:17.250
at the destruction, that is facing us from within and without.

00:28:17.458 --> 00:28:21.166
We see diseases like cancer and other horrible diseases,

00:28:21.417 --> 00:28:22.875
which we cannot combat.

00:28:23.041 --> 00:28:28.333
We see the problems of the nations and political, economic crises,

00:28:28.583 --> 00:28:32.667
and we don't understand how to control it on individual basis.

00:28:32.917 --> 00:28:37.291
All these things can only be solved if you become the Spirit.

00:28:37.500 --> 00:28:42.375
The Spirit is within you the link with the whole.

00:28:42.667 --> 00:28:46.999
Like the microcosm, the whole, you are a part and parcel of that.

00:28:47.166 --> 00:28:49.709
Like my finger is part and parcel of the whole.

00:28:49.959 --> 00:28:54.000
Now, if there is pain in my finger, I can feel the whole.

00:28:54.208 --> 00:28:57.291
In the same way once I become aware of My Spirit,

00:28:57.542 --> 00:29:01.417
I can feel the whole, I become collectively conscious.

00:29:01.625 --> 00:29:04.792
I do not talk about it, I do not say that

00:29:04.999 --> 00:29:08.542
'You are now brothers and sisters', but it just happens that

00:29:08.750 --> 00:29:12.375
on your fingertips you start feeling others, very clearly,

00:29:12.583 --> 00:29:15.041
their centres, their problems, your problems

00:29:15.250 --> 00:29:19.250
and also you know methods how to clear it out.

00:29:19.458 --> 00:29:22.208
Compassion people talk of, of giving compassion,

00:29:22.417 --> 00:29:24.834
looking after people and doing good to them.

00:29:25.083 --> 00:29:29.208
But this compassion talks, it doesn't solve the problem.

00:29:29.417 --> 00:29:33.458
But the compassion that flows from you, works. It works out.

00:29:33.709 --> 00:29:37.709
It helps people in a way that they are not aware of it.

00:29:37.917 --> 00:29:40.917
For example in India we had one Indian,

00:29:41.083 --> 00:29:42.750
who got realisation in a village.

00:29:42.959 --> 00:29:45.000
He was a farmer, he went back,

00:29:45.208 --> 00:29:49.583
and he gave realisation to so many people, and it is unbelievable,

00:29:49.792 --> 00:29:56.291
how he could manage such a lot of population to come to Sahaja Yoga.

00:29:56.542 --> 00:29:58.667
But he told Me that certain incidents

00:29:58.875 --> 00:30:05.083
like, 'A man came to me and he was an alcoholic,

00:30:05.417 --> 00:30:08.417
and he came to me and he was about to beat me.

00:30:08.667 --> 00:30:10.875
But I was very quiet. I just told him,

00:30:11.041 --> 00:30:13.125
"Now don't beat me, you sit down for a while".

00:30:13.375 --> 00:30:17.041
He sat down and after some time, I awakened his Kundalini.

00:30:17.250 --> 00:30:19.917
Overnight he gave up alcohol!

00:30:20.250 --> 00:30:21.792
Overnight he gave it up.

00:30:21.999 --> 00:30:23.875
He became like a king. He said, "What?

00:30:24.041 --> 00:30:25.750
I'm not going to drink anymore".'

00:30:25.959 --> 00:30:31.375
It's not mental, but just he achieved his supreme thing,

00:30:31.709 --> 00:30:38.500
the highest thing, his purpose and the whole being got glorified.

00:30:38.709 --> 00:30:42.333
So you start feeling your own powers.

00:30:42.542 --> 00:30:45.875
Actually when you go to any guru, you must also find out

00:30:46.041 --> 00:30:49.959
from the disciples, if they have achieved any powers or not.

00:30:50.125 --> 00:30:52.834
It is not important if a guru says, "I am such and such".

00:30:53.000 --> 00:30:57.709
For example, the lady who came to interview Me, she said,

00:30:57.917 --> 00:31:01.208
"Do You think you are the highest saint of India?" and all that.

00:31:01.417 --> 00:31:05.417
I said, "I never said so. But the saints in India do say so."

00:31:05.625 --> 00:31:08.291
All right. If you believe in it or not makes no difference.

00:31:08.542 --> 00:31:11.291
It is for you to find out. But leave alone Me,

00:31:11.500 --> 00:31:14.417
why not find out about yourself, what happens to you.

00:31:14.625 --> 00:31:19.208
Supposing you become the saint, supposing you have the powers,

00:31:19.417 --> 00:31:22.375
supposing you manifest that compassion which I am talking of,

00:31:22.583 --> 00:31:25.792
then you have to believe that there is something about yourself.

00:31:25.999 --> 00:31:28.500
First of all you all must have faith in yourselves,

00:31:28.709 --> 00:31:32.417
that you are capable of becoming that Self,

00:31:32.625 --> 00:31:36.291
which is collectively conscious to begin with,

00:31:36.667 --> 00:31:41.917
which is the source of all the joy, health, wealth

00:31:42.083 --> 00:31:44.834
and all kinds of satisfaction,

00:31:45.083 --> 00:31:49.458
and the one which is the witness of the play of Divine,

00:31:49.667 --> 00:31:55.750
the one that allows you to transmit this Divine power to others.

00:31:55.999 --> 00:31:59.250
After realisation, for example Dr. Warren himself

00:31:59.542 --> 00:32:01.750
was very reluctant in the beginning.

00:32:01.959 --> 00:32:04.208
He was a difficult person to begin with.

00:32:04.417 --> 00:32:06.083
Then he got his realisation

00:32:06.291 --> 00:32:09.125
and after realisation he was quite satisfied.

00:32:09.333 --> 00:32:11.125
Because he had been to so many gurus.

00:32:11.333 --> 00:32:13.125
There's no guru he had not been.

00:32:13.333 --> 00:32:20.166
And he was so angry and aggressive when he came to Sahaja Yoga.

00:32:20.417 --> 00:32:25.458
When he got into realisation, he just felt that he has found it.

00:32:25.709 --> 00:32:29.625
Now, through him in Australia we have established

00:32:29.834 --> 00:32:33.166
so many centres, and so many people have got realisation.

00:32:33.375 --> 00:32:35.959
It's a surprising thing that one man,

00:32:36.125 --> 00:32:40.041
who reluctantly came to Me on a telephone number,

00:32:40.333 --> 00:32:43.834
has suddenly become such an enlightened person,

00:32:44.000 --> 00:32:47.625
that he has given realisation to so many people,

00:32:47.917 --> 00:32:50.917
and to whom he has given realisation, have

00:32:51.083 --> 00:32:53.750
also given Realisation to so many others.

00:32:53.959 --> 00:32:57.875
Apart from that they have cured diseases like cancer

00:32:58.041 --> 00:33:02.542
and all kinds of serious diseases we talk about. It's a fact.

00:33:02.750 --> 00:33:06.250
For this you cannot pay. That's one thing for sure.

00:33:06.458 --> 00:33:08.458
You cannot pay for it. It's all free.

00:33:08.667 --> 00:33:11.999
As this nature is free to give you everything

00:33:12.166 --> 00:33:14.792
that is essential and vital within you.

00:33:14.999 --> 00:33:20.125
In the same way this knowledge has to be without any effort.

00:33:20.375 --> 00:33:24.083
Supposing if we have to learn about breathing,

00:33:24.291 --> 00:33:28.083
going to a library, how many of us would survive?

00:33:28.333 --> 00:33:32.083
It is so vital that it has to be the easiest, the simplest

00:33:32.291 --> 00:33:35.250
and everything that is living is so simple,

00:33:35.458 --> 00:33:39.250
that we don't also bother to think about it.

00:33:39.458 --> 00:33:43.500
We take all this for granted.

00:33:44.333 --> 00:33:47.667
The subject is very wide.

00:33:47.999 --> 00:33:50.500
It has many aspects and dimensions.

00:33:50.709 --> 00:33:55.041
First when the Kundalini rises, it crosses through this center,

00:33:55.291 --> 00:33:57.792
which is called as the Agnya chakra,

00:33:57.999 --> 00:34:02.583
which is the chakra of our Lord Jesus Christ.

00:34:02.792 --> 00:34:05.291
Tomorrow I'll be telling you the names of all the deities,

00:34:05.500 --> 00:34:07.500
who reside on these centers.

00:34:07.709 --> 00:34:10.125
Now it is difficult for a scientist to accept,

00:34:10.333 --> 00:34:14.375
that there are deities who are sitting on these chakras.

00:34:14.583 --> 00:34:18.792
But Socrates and Confucius who were such ancient people,

00:34:18.999 --> 00:34:22.792
have talked about these Gods, that we have to keep them pleased

00:34:23.000 --> 00:34:24.875
and you have to keep them all right.

00:34:25.041 --> 00:34:27.583
But those realised souls perhaps you don't know.

00:34:27.792 --> 00:34:32.375
That's not easy to convince human beings who are not realised souls

00:34:32.583 --> 00:34:37.000
about these deities being within you.

00:34:37.333 --> 00:34:40.041
And they are all just waiting there.

00:34:40.291 --> 00:34:45.792
As soon as the Kundalini rises you start manifesting your grandeur,

00:34:45.999 --> 00:34:48.917
your great personality that awaits you.

00:34:49.125 --> 00:34:52.667
This is something not fantastic to Me,

00:34:52.875 --> 00:34:56.917
because I've seen thousands of people getting realisation,

00:34:57.125 --> 00:34:59.709
thousands of them feeling the cool breeze,

00:34:59.999 --> 00:35:02.458
thousands of them transforming.

00:35:02.709 --> 00:35:05.709
Another thing one has to see in a person, in a guru,

00:35:05.917 --> 00:35:08.041
when you go to a guru, that

00:35:08.250 --> 00:35:12.000
'Is this the man giving any transformation to another person?'

00:35:12.208 --> 00:35:15.417
Here they are, they are smuggling, they are telling lies,

00:35:15.625 --> 00:35:17.583
they are killing people and they have a guru.

00:35:17.792 --> 00:35:18.875
How can you have a guru,

00:35:19.041 --> 00:35:22.166
when you are doing all these anti-God activities?

00:35:22.375 --> 00:35:24.458
All kinds of anti-God activities they are doing:

00:35:24.667 --> 00:35:30.208
They are hot-tempered, they are liars, they are intriguers,

00:35:30.458 --> 00:35:32.750
all sorts of things they'll be doing

00:35:32.959 --> 00:35:35.792
and they will be saying that "We have a guru".

00:35:36.000 --> 00:35:38.875
What's the use of such a guru, who allows you to do these things?

00:35:39.041 --> 00:35:41.834
It's better not to have such a guru who allows you to do that.

00:35:42.041 --> 00:35:44.875
Secondly, a guru if you have a real one,

00:35:45.041 --> 00:35:48.000
he has to look after your health, minimum of minimum.

00:35:48.208 --> 00:35:51.375
But if you go to a guru and if you get epilepsy

00:35:51.583 --> 00:35:54.709
or if you go to a guru and you get a bad head

00:35:54.917 --> 00:35:57.166
or some sort of a headache, then he says,

00:35:57.375 --> 00:36:00.041
"All right, these are your sins, you better suffer".

00:36:00.250 --> 00:36:02.125
So one should ask a question to such a guru,

00:36:02.333 --> 00:36:06.583
that, "Then why are you there? Why are we paying you for?

00:36:06.792 --> 00:36:10.208
If you can't even look after our health,what are we paying you for?"

00:36:10.417 --> 00:36:13.291
There could be a guru who can teach you something,

00:36:13.500 --> 00:36:15.542
like he'll say that, "I'll make you fly".

00:36:15.750 --> 00:36:17.875
So you must ask the guru to fly himself.

00:36:18.083 --> 00:36:20.166
If the guru can fly, then you pay him.

00:36:20.375 --> 00:36:22.959
What's the use of paying a guru who just says, you can fly.

00:36:23.125 --> 00:36:25.834
"All right, you give me six thousand pounds, I'll make you fly."

00:36:26.000 --> 00:36:28.917
Better ask the guru to fly and see that he flies.

00:36:29.083 --> 00:36:31.542
But people are so identified with the gurus,

00:36:31.750 --> 00:36:35.583
that despite they become absolutely bankrupt, finished,

00:36:35.792 --> 00:36:38.709
gone cases, still they are sticking on to these gurus,

00:36:38.999 --> 00:36:40.000
because they are mesmerised.

00:36:40.208 --> 00:36:43.000
They don't want to have their own Self-realisation,

00:36:43.208 --> 00:36:45.250
they don't want to have their own powers,

00:36:45.458 --> 00:36:48.875
but they want to abide by the so-called powers of their guru

00:36:49.041 --> 00:36:52.750
and all these things. They become absolutely hopeless cases,

00:36:52.999 --> 00:36:55.917
gone cases, good for nothing, lost people,

00:36:56.083 --> 00:36:59.250
but still they'll stick on to these people and

00:36:59.458 --> 00:37:03.417
will continue with it till they are perished as useless cabbages.

