And by Kriya Yoga you cannot get  realisation.

00:53:36.000 --> 00:53:37.500
There is no Kriya Yoga.

00:53:37.709 --> 00:53:40.291
In no traditional book it is there, no traditional.

00:53:40.500 --> 00:53:42.709
This is a new thing started by people,

00:53:42.917 --> 00:53:45.458
they used to even cut the tongues of people,

00:53:45.667 --> 00:53:48.458
say that you put it back here, put the tracheae,

00:53:48.667 --> 00:53:51.208
do all kinds of things. There are many people in India who have

00:53:51.417 --> 00:53:56.792
their tongues waving like dogs, who have been to Kriya.

00:53:56.999 --> 00:53:59.333
There's no such things needed at all.

00:53:59.542 --> 00:54:01.208
It is spontaneous, it is within you,

00:54:01.417 --> 00:54:04.667
you don't have to do anything about it. That is what it is!

00:54:04.917 --> 00:54:06.083
Absolutely!

00:54:06.291 --> 00:54:08.667
You don't have to do anything, you don't have to stand on your head,

00:54:08.875 --> 00:54:11.250
or nothing at all. It's just simple.

00:54:11.458 --> 00:54:14.041
So Kriya Yoga is not sahaja.

00:54:14.250 --> 00:54:15.709
'Is not sahaja' means

00:54:15.917 --> 00:54:19.291
'saha' means 'with' and 'ja' is 'born'. It's spontaneous.

00:54:19.500 --> 00:54:22.583
It is a spontaneous thing, you don't have to do anything about it.

00:54:22.792 --> 00:54:25.208
Nothing.

00:54:26.083 --> 00:54:30.875
But once you get it, once you get it, you can give it to others.

00:54:31.041 --> 00:54:33.625
It's like if you know how to swim

00:54:33.834 --> 00:54:37.291
and if there's somebody who does not know and he is getting drowned.

00:54:37.500 --> 00:54:38.834
What you tell that person, that

00:54:39.000 --> 00:54:41.583
"You keep quiet just now, I'll take you to the shore".

00:54:41.792 --> 00:54:43.166
Then you are brought to the shore

00:54:43.375 --> 00:54:46.959
and you teach him how to swim, and then he can save others also.

00:54:47.125 --> 00:54:49.000
But the one who does not know how to swim,

00:54:49.208 --> 00:54:53.917
has to do nothing for the time being, just to get his realisation,

00:54:54.083 --> 00:54:57.083
mature in it and then give realisation to others.

00:54:57.291 --> 00:55:00.375
No Kriya is needed at all in Sahaja Yoga.

00:55:00.583 --> 00:55:02.291
Actually it is not at all traditional.

00:55:02.500 --> 00:55:04.709
It is a very recent stuff that has come out.

00:55:04.917 --> 00:55:07.875
If you read from the past, if you read Adi Shankaracharya,

00:55:08.041 --> 00:55:10.709
the sixth century, if you read other people, Markandeya like,

00:55:10.917 --> 00:55:13.542
fourteenth century, you'll be amazed, that

00:55:13.750 --> 00:55:17.208
they have said the same thing what I am saying; this is traditional.

00:55:17.417 --> 00:55:21.291
But these new gurus came up, they started talking about this and that,

00:55:21.500 --> 00:55:22.959
but it is not so.

00:55:23.166 --> 00:55:25.999
Nobody can achieve realisation by Kriya Yoga.

00:55:26.208 --> 00:55:29.250
I've not met one. On the contrary they come to Me as patients.

00:55:29.542 --> 00:55:32.417
I must say, I'm sorry to say, but it is so.

00:55:32.625 --> 00:55:34.250
People have spent so much money,

00:55:34.458 --> 00:55:38.375
from India they have gone all the way to America to do Kriya Yoga

00:55:38.625 --> 00:55:41.500
and they are just suffering. Nobody has achieved anything.

00:55:41.709 --> 00:55:43.834
So now whatever you have done, it's finished.

00:55:44.000 --> 00:55:46.750
Now you be interested in yourself and in your seeking.

00:55:46.999 --> 00:55:49.041
Just forget it whatever you have done.

00:55:49.250 --> 00:55:50.625
Now what you have to do is,

00:55:50.834 --> 00:55:53.625
to just get your realisation and work it out.

00:55:53.834 --> 00:55:56.375
Forget it whatever you have been doing,

00:55:56.583 --> 00:55:58.625
because you have not yet achieved the result.

00:55:58.834 --> 00:55:59.709
So forget it!

00:55:59.917 --> 00:56:03.709
And see for yourself without any Kriya you receive it or not.

00:56:03.917 --> 00:56:05.875
It is all described but the trouble is,

00:56:06.041 --> 00:56:10.041
all the Sanskrit books which are authentic are not being translated.

00:56:10.250 --> 00:56:12.625
So it's not traditional at all.

00:56:12.834 --> 00:56:16.458
Christ never said you have to do anything like that.

00:56:16.709 --> 00:56:20.125
Nobody has said it. Everybody has talked of spontaneous happening.

00:56:20.375 --> 00:56:24.625
Even Martin Luther, when he tried to change people from Catholicism,

00:56:24.834 --> 00:56:26.542
he talked of spontaneity.

00:56:26.834 --> 00:56:29.333
He was also a realised soul, but later on his followers

00:56:29.542 --> 00:56:31.333
tried to make a mess of everything.

00:56:31.625 --> 00:56:34.083
In the same way Christ also talked of the same thing.

00:56:34.291 --> 00:56:36.583
Did they say that you have to stand on your head, cut your tongues,

00:56:36.792 --> 00:56:38.417
put them back, push it back?

00:56:38.625 --> 00:56:41.208
All these things are absolutely not to be done.

00:56:41.417 --> 00:56:44.667
It's very harmful, one should never do it.

00:56:53.208 --> 00:56:55.750
So let us have now the experiment, all right?

00:56:55.999 --> 00:56:57.333
All of you are seekers.

00:56:57.542 --> 00:57:00.917
Now forget what you have been doing, what is done, forget it.

00:57:01.083 --> 00:57:02.500
Because you have been -

00:57:02.709 --> 00:57:05.834
you have to be kind to yourself, to be truthful to yourself,

00:57:06.125 --> 00:57:07.250
you have to be your Self.

00:57:07.500 --> 00:57:10.834
I'm the only person who'll say that you have to get to it.

00:57:11.000 --> 00:57:13.500
If you don't get it, I will not rest and you should not rest.

00:57:13.709 --> 00:57:16.542
If I have patience for you, you should also have patience for you.

00:57:16.834 --> 00:57:19.709
Don't be angry with anyone, don't be angry with yourself,

00:57:19.959 --> 00:57:21.125
don't be angry with your gurus,

00:57:21.333 --> 00:57:23.750
whatever has happened has happened, doesn't matter.

00:57:23.959 --> 00:57:28.875
You'll be amazed, I Myself get surprised the way Divine is working.

00:57:29.083 --> 00:57:32.959
Whatever you may do it, whatever may be the problems, it works,

00:57:33.125 --> 00:57:34.709
it works, really it works.

00:57:34.917 --> 00:57:36.667
It's something so amazing.

00:57:36.875 --> 00:57:38.917
It is better that you see to it, that you get it.

00:57:39.083 --> 00:57:40.917
Because you are seekers of ages.

00:57:41.083 --> 00:57:44.625
This is not a life you are wasting, you have been seeking for ages.

00:57:44.834 --> 00:57:48.667
And today the time has come, that's why you are here to get it.

00:57:48.917 --> 00:57:51.792
So please just get your realisation. Forget the past.

00:57:52.000 --> 00:57:56.583
May God bless you all.

00:58:12.208 --> 00:58:14.625
I would request you for a simple thing:

00:58:14.834 --> 00:58:15.917
we have to take out our shoes,

00:58:16.083 --> 00:58:18.375
because the Mother Earth also takes away our problems.

00:58:18.583 --> 00:58:20.583
She's very helpful. Even the light is helpful.

00:58:20.792 --> 00:58:23.291
Now some people ask, "Why the light?" Even this little light

00:58:23.500 --> 00:58:26.917
is so helpful, if it is there. Just take out your shoes.

00:58:27.166 --> 00:58:31.917
Just to take help from the Mother Earth. It's very simple.

00:58:32.250 --> 00:58:36.000
Now you have to put your both the hands towards Me like this

00:58:36.250 --> 00:58:37.375
in a very simple way.

00:58:37.625 --> 00:58:39.166
First of all you should be comfortably seated.

00:58:39.375 --> 00:58:40.999
There should be no discomfort,

00:58:41.166 --> 00:58:43.750
so that when it is happening you again get distracted.

00:58:43.959 --> 00:58:47.250
Just to sit comfortably, have easy sitting,

00:58:47.458 --> 00:58:55.375
no, no tightening in the neck or in the -

00:58:56.291 --> 00:58:57.959
I mean uncomfortable tightening.

00:58:58.125 --> 00:59:00.834
It's all right, if you can feel comfortable.
